_Division__c}                        </td>                    </tr>                    <tr>                        <td>Business Unit</td>                        <td>: &nbsp; {!RelatedTo.ASI_TnE_Business_Unit__c}                        </td>                    </tr>                    <tr>                        <td>Type of Expense Claim</td>                        <td>: &nbsp; {!RelatedTo.ASI_TnE_Type__c}                        </td>                    </tr>                    <tr>                        <td>Remarks</td>                        <td>: &nbsp; {!RelatedTo.ASI_TnE_Remarks__c}                        </td>                    </tr>                    <tr>                        <td>Finance Remarks</td>                        <td>: &nbsp; {!RelatedTo.ASI_TnE_Finance_Remarks__c}                        </td>                    </tr>                </table><p>You can click this&nbsp;<apex:outputLink value="{!LEFT($Api.Partner_Server_URL_140, FIND('.com/',$Api.Partner_Server_URL_140)+3)}/{!RelatedTo.id}">link</apex:outputLink> to access the claim for details.</p>            </body>        </html>    </messaging:htmlEmailBody></messaging:emailTemplate>